reviewText: Growing up I always loved watching the show with my Mother.  Now that she is no longer with me, the video is more special to me!  I thank the seller for the wonderful service that was given to me ~ A ++++

My children in our child development program really enjoyed Rudolph the Red Nosed Reindeer. This VHS tape was a true steal. They wanted to watch it everyday. We do allow these movies on special days. I love the price and will purchase more from this company.
except for the Grinch, maybe.  Enjoyed by kids and adults alike.  It  teaches children that it's OK to be different.  A great movie!

I LOVE Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer, Fun for the entire family, great songs, and a great lesson - never judge by the color of one's nose because everyone has a place, even misfits!  I'm 24 and in law school, but I still  love it!
